OL,3,C31 charged after large scale riots in
OL,4,CEly
OL,6,FThe large scale disorder began shortly
OL,7,Fafter the collision and lasted several
OL,8,Fhours with property damaged and cars
OL,9,Fset alight.
OL,11,FAn investigation by the Independent
OL,12,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC) into
OL,13,Fthe actions of police officers in the
OL,14,Flead up to teenagers' deaths is
OL,15,Fongoing.
OL,17,FThe driver and the passenger of the
OL,18,Fpolice van have both been previously
OL,19,Fserved with a gross misconduct notice.
