OL,6,FChief Superintendent of South Wales
OL,7,FPolice said the disorder left people
OL,8,Fscared in their own homes.
OL,10,FSpeaking on today's charges Danny
OL,11,FRichards thanked people in Ely: "We
OL,12,Fare extremely grateful for the support
OL,13,Ffrom the community throughout our
OL,14,Finvestigation and we now await the
OL,15,Foutcome of the court process."
OL,17,FThe Crown Prosecution Service has
OL,18,Freminded people not to speculate
OL,19,Fonline: "Criminal proceedings against
OL,20,Fthese individuals are now active and
OL,21,Fthey have a right to a fair trial.
